1.00	Little_Giant_Ladder_System	Wing Enterprises	Wing Enterprises is a Springville, Utah company, and the largest manufacturer of American-made ladders. The company produces the Little Giant Ladder System, a convertible aluminium ladder system. The founder of Wing Enterprises, Harold Ray Wing (aka Hal Wing), came across a prototype of the ladder in Germany in the 1970s. He patented the design in the United States and began manufacturing the ladder in his home and selling it at trade shows.	
